3 November 2008Minister in The Presidency Dr Manto Tshabalala-Msimang will visit two disability centres in Soshanguve as part of government s programme to improve the lives of people with disabilities. During the visit the Minister will also distribute agricultural starter packs.The details are: Members of the media are invited to cover the event as per programme below:Session 1Briefing Session: Principals of the two centres, SGB, OSDP officials and Councillor Session 2Enquiries Peter Moloi Cell: 082 569 2533Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)